title: The Adventures of Baby Jaimie
description: Come follow Baby Jaimie on her very first adventure. In this story, Baby Jaimie gets her first wheelchair and discovers things she can now do with her chair that she couldn't do before like playing baseball and racing her family and friends. By learning she can now do the things that other children can do she also learns that in her chair she is unstoppable and learns to believe in herself.
author: Jaimie Hope
